\f6\fs24 \cf0 \cb1 \strokec9 Intended Use or Purpose is defined in Clause 3.6 as
\f7\i \'a0
\f8\b 'use for which a product, process or service is intended according to the specifications, instructions and information provided by the manufacturer.\'92
\f9\i0 \
