\f5\b \cf5 \cb3 \strokec5 device, whether used alone or in combination, intended by the\'a0manufacturer for the in-vitro examination of specimens derived from the human body solely or principally to provide information for diagnostic, monitoring or compatibility purposes and including reagents, calibrators, control materials, specimen receptacles, software, and related instruments or apparatus or other articles .'
